articles.title: Typhoon Yagi collapses busy bridge in Vietnam - BBC.com
articles.description: Typhoon Yagi, the most powerful to hit Asia this year, kills 60 and destroys homes across north of country.
articles.content:
Footage online showed part of the 375-metre Phong Chau bridge still standing
